The '''Valley of Ternaax''' was once a beautiful forested valley on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Rannon]].

Sometime after the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] and the execution of [[Order 66/Legends|Order 66]], [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] [[Danaan Kerr]] settled in the Valley of Ternaax. Sensing a disturbance in the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] of [[The Force/Legends|the Force]], Kerr began terrorizing many of Rannon's inhabitants and training several in the ways of the dark side. As a result of Kerr's actions, the once-beautiful valley rotted and lost its former beauty.

